description:
&lt;p&gt;There are few careers that are as rewarding as one at Derbyshire Healthcare.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Here you will have the opportunity to support people of all backgrounds and ages.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As Personal Secretary to the Radbourne Unit Area Service Manager and providing administrative support to the wider leadership team, you will embark on a role that provides good variety across a range of duties. You will also be an integral support to ensuring good organisation amongst our friendly and energetic team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will have excellent IT, organisational, interpersonal and communication skills and be able to work under pressure and on your own initiative.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This position will allow you to work to your full potential within an administrative role and we are keen to support ongoing learning and development opportunities for all our staff.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hannah Burton, ASM, at hannahburton1@nhs.net or on 01332 623700.&lt;/p&gt;
